Text: RE Easter Sundayshendrinsf I wanna eat a nice big juicey steak and potato tonight interested Rayfael Roman GHG Corporation Original Message From mailto Sent Thursday April PM To ROMAN RAYFAEL JSCNT RAY Subject Easter Sunday In order to do something semiEaster related we have brunch reservations at am on Sunday at Commanders Palace in the Aladdin Jim will already be gone but I think everybody else will still be around I took the liberty of making the reservations because it will probably fill up Easter and all Scott
